&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Senior Managers are high-agency leadership roles for senior learning operators who thrive in complex, live environments. They take responsibility for propagating delivery fidelity, staff and student outcomes, and retention and impact success at scale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
