&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This role builds vibrant systems capacity by establishing delivery norms, patterns, standards, and expectations that cascade through managers, instructors, and fellows—enabling programs to scale without loss of quality, coherence, or trust.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
